column5: Just wondering if anyone has been out to Moira Lake recently and has any information on ice conditions?   Don't feel like swimming on Sunday!  Thanks.
some of us can't get out as much as we think we should be allowed and when that opportunity hits ,,, yeah a bit of info goes  along way .lookin' at the same empty glass with lake st.john.
I'll be out too on Moira but not sure about the ice thickness.
I've heard stories of some big muskie in Moira lake as well as quite a bit of pike and walleye. Any truth to this?? I've got a buddy with a trailer there and an open invite to go this summer.
